# Ignore ALL of vlan-images/ by default. Only the redacted, post-referenced
# images are force-added (git add -f) into commits. This guarantees the
# UN-redacted originals never get committed: the _orig_backup/ and
# _redact_backup/ folders, the raw honey_*/vlan_* upload dumps, and the
# unreferenced spare screenshots all hold pre-redaction serverGuid / cert
# fingerprint / admin-UPN data.
vlan-images/*

# Generated publish artifacts
_build-vlan18-draft.md
*-PREVIEW.docx
